        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Extremely accurate for English and major languages. In my testing, the auto captions consistently achieved 95%+ accuracy on clear speech, with proper punctuation and timing. You can edit any mistakes directly in the caption editor. The AI also handles multiple speakers and adjusts caption styling automatically for readability.",
            "marks": []
          }
